description:
TENA Extra Long Length Liner is specifically designed to manage the thin, fast flow of light bladder leakage. It offers effective absorbency whilst offering extra security and coverage so you can enjoy everyday activities. Ideal if you prefer the additional coverage of an extra long length liner.

  • Features TENA Triple Protection against leaks, odour and moisture. 
  • BodyFit™ shape contours to the body for added security.
  • Soft, breathable top sheet for ultimate comfort.
  • Packed in a box for convenient bathroom storage and minimal packaging.

Recommended for:

  • Extra long length, coverage and absorbency
  • Very light urge incontinence – a sudden need to get to the toilet
  • Frequent stress incontinence when laughing coughing or sneezing
  • More strenuous sports such as tennis or netball, to last the entire game
name: Tena Liners Extra Long 24 Pack
